        answer: "Superficial peels produce immediate brightening, with full results visible within a week. Medium-depth peels show significant improvement once peeling is complete, around day seven to ten, with continued improvement over the following month as new collagen forms. The most dramatic results from any peel continue to develop for four to six weeks after treatment."
